   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Nikephoros, agent of Alexander, to Pasoknopaios, associate of Harphaesis, greetings. I have received from you, of the price of the wine, four artabas; of the price of nine and one-half artabas which he owes, I have four artabas of grain (equals) 4 artabas. Year 16, Pauni 12."</ab>
